==Objects for Worship== The principal [[Shintai|objects of worship]] (''shintai'') at the shrine are {{ill|Shitateruhime|ja|下照比売|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shitateruhime|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to シタテルヒメ}} and [[Ame no Wakahiko]]. The two gods are understood as a wife and husband.
== Access == The entrance station to this shrine is the [[:en:Mefu-jinja Station|Mefu-jinja Station]] on the [[:en:Hankyu Takarazuka Line|Hankyu Takarazuka Line]]. {{Shinto-stub}}
